query:
SELECT 
  id,
  nome,
  dum,
  dataUltrassom,
  igUltrassomSemanas,
  igUltrassomDias,
  CASE 
    WHEN dum IS NULL THEN 'DUM NULL'
    WHEN dum = '' THEN 'DUM VAZIO'
    WHEN dum LIKE '0000%' THEN 'DUM INVÁLIDA'
    ELSE 'DUM OK'
  END as status_dum,
  CASE 
    WHEN dataUltrassom IS NULL THEN 'US NULL'
    WHEN dataUltrassom = '' THEN 'US VAZIO'
    WHEN dataUltrassom LIKE '0000%' THEN 'US INVÁLIDA'
    ELSE 'US OK'
  END as status_us
FROM gestantes 
WHERE email = 'teste@gestantesapp.com';
